          "vnum": 91,
          "name": "Burning Pit",
          "description": "Barely large enough for a body, the pit within the meditation chamber is filled with slowly, softly burning coals beneath a thick layer of chalky ash. Your flesh begins to sear in the heat. The walls are cracked stone, steam pouring out of the breaks.",
