          "description": "You stand within a broad, low chamber. A muted red seeps through thin black cloaks which cover glowing globes; a quintet of them evenly spaced along the walls. Within a charred diamond-shaped pit in the centre of the chamber burns a heady, pungent sacrament. The ceiling is plain earth, having been left open to allow the roots of the forest above to dangle, dry, and die in the arid room.",
